It was more comfortable than I expected, so I was flustered.

1819
01:20:13,908 --> 01:20:15,078
- Really?
- Yes.

1820
01:20:15,408 --> 01:20:17,568
But it's not easy to feel comfortable around Hee Dong.

1821
01:20:18,648 --> 01:20:20,978
- Really?
- Yes.

1822
01:20:29,088 --> 01:20:31,218
What are you worried about?

1823
01:20:31,758 --> 01:20:32,888
What I'm worried about?

1824
01:20:33,528 --> 01:20:35,858
Si Woo wants to know what's on Yu Bin's heart.

1825
01:20:37,198 --> 01:20:38,528
You can be honest.

1826
01:20:39,598 --> 01:20:41,228
To be honest,

1827
01:20:41,428 --> 01:20:44,338
I like someone dark and strong.

1828
01:20:44,808 --> 01:20:48,208
After all, he meets my ideal type.

1829
01:20:48,478 --> 01:20:50,978
I'd always wanted to go on a date with him at least once.

1830
01:20:51,208 --> 01:20:53,148
I liked him, so I asked him.

1831
01:20:53,448 --> 01:20:55,548
But we were comfortable like friends.

1832
01:20:57,048 --> 01:20:59,448
But I'm not sure...

1833
01:20:59,948 --> 01:21:05,088
whether he expressed his feelings like a joke or not.

1834
01:21:07,858 --> 01:21:11,828
Don't you think there's a way you felt that way?

1835
01:21:12,128 --> 01:21:15,638
I don't think...

1836
01:21:15,968 --> 01:21:18,368
he completely shut me out.

1837
01:21:18,468 --> 01:21:20,338
- I see.
- I thought we became close.

1838
01:21:20,668 --> 01:21:24,137
When I said, "You don't remember..."

1839
01:21:24,138 --> 01:21:25,347
"what I said yesterday."

1840
01:21:25,348 --> 01:21:28,477
He said, "I lose my memories in front of the person I like."

1841
01:21:28,478 --> 01:21:30,017
That's what he said.

1842
01:21:30,018 --> 01:21:31,048
What?

1843
01:21:32,048 --> 01:21:33,547
But that's...

1844
01:21:33,548 --> 01:21:37,017
That happened while we were on a date.

1845
01:21:37,018 --> 01:21:38,428
In a way,

1846
01:21:38,658 --> 01:21:41,428
I wonder if he expressed himself.

1847
01:21:43,358 --> 01:21:44,868
I don't know what's on his mind.

1848
01:21:46,668 --> 01:21:48,797
- He confused her.
- Exactly.

1849
01:21:48,798 --> 01:21:51,907
It's normal for my daughter to be confused.

1850
01:21:51,908 --> 01:21:53,108
Obviously, she's confused.

1851
01:21:54,638 --> 01:21:56,008
I don't know what's on his mind.

1852
01:22:00,108 --> 01:22:01,147
What?

1853
01:22:01,148 --> 01:22:03,148
(What?)

1854
01:22:03,548 --> 01:22:05,488
I kept thinking, "What?"

1855
01:22:09,318 --> 01:22:12,058
I kept thinking about what Hee Dong's like.

1856
01:22:12,288 --> 01:22:14,728
If he said that considering what he's like,

1857
01:22:15,958 --> 01:22:17,358
what was he thinking?

1858
01:22:19,728 --> 01:22:22,598
What was on his mind when he said that?

1859
01:22:23,238 --> 01:22:25,208
I kept thinking about that.

1860
01:22:26,308 --> 01:22:30,277
I'm not sure if Hee Dong was...

1861
01:22:30,278 --> 01:22:31,538
expressing his feelings.

1862
01:22:31,948 --> 01:22:33,708
No wonder you're confused.

1863
01:22:34,078 --> 01:22:36,848
- But how did that come up?
- That's what I mean.

1864
01:22:37,448 --> 01:22:38,488
I don't know.

1865
01:22:39,518 --> 01:22:41,488
- Gosh, this is really hard.
- I know.

1866
01:22:41,658 --> 01:22:44,557
I was thinking this is an unexpected variable.

1867
01:22:44,558 --> 01:22:45,827
I can't even guess.

1868
01:22:45,828 --> 01:22:48,188
(A confusing night)

1869
01:22:48,498 --> 01:22:52,368
I'm kind of anxious...

1870
01:22:52,968 --> 01:22:56,168
because I can never guess where Hee Dong would go.

1871
01:22:57,968 --> 01:23:01,538
(Women are confused.)

1872
01:23:02,438 --> 01:23:05,978
(And the man who is hard to read)

1873
01:23:07,108 --> 01:23:13,048
(What's going to happen to their relationship?)

1874
01:23:14,133 --> 01:23:16,373
(I think I'm certain now. I was very nervous.)

1875
01:23:17,173 --> 01:23:18,612
(Two daughters' hearts...)

1876
01:23:18,613 --> 01:23:20,473
(for the same person)

1877
01:23:21,313 --> 01:23:25,382
(I want to spend the rest of my time here on one person.)

1878
01:23:25,383 --> 01:23:27,713
- Don't just sit on your hands.
- Yes, go for it.

1879
01:23:27,813 --> 01:23:29,783
(I was worried about Yu Bin.)

1880
01:23:30,453 --> 01:23:33,052
(Anxiety...)

1881
01:23:33,053 --> 01:23:34,952
(and new excitement)

1882
01:23:34,953 --> 01:23:36,622
All I could think about was your cream pasta.

1883
01:23:36,623 --> 01:23:38,193
- Stop. Enough.
- What?

1884
01:23:38,533 --> 01:23:40,132
(In a changed atmosphere, )

1885
01:23:40,133 --> 01:23:41,462
(the two cross.)

1886
01:23:41,463 --> 01:23:44,832
(Their relationship is unpredictable.)

1887
01:23:44,833 --> 01:23:46,633
- Something got messed up.
- What's going on?

1888
01:23:47,497 --> 01:23:49,497
Dramaday.me
